Package com.petpet.c3po.api.model.helper

This package contains some helper model classes of C3PO that do not have to be serialized to the back-end data store, but are used by the core module.

          Description

Interface Summary
MetadataStream This interface abstracts a gathered resource that is passed for parsing to the adaptors.

BetweenFilterCondition A filter condition that represent a between x and y condition, e.g.
Filter This class is used to define a filter for a c3po data model class.
FilterCondition Encapsulates a single filter condition of a filter.
MetadataRecord A single metadata record of an element.
NumericStatistics A simple object that encapsulates the results of some simple statistical calculations over the values of a numeric property.
 

Enum Summary
BetweenFilterCondition.Operator The different supported operators.
MetadataRecord.Status The status of the element shows the certainty with which the value for the given property is correct.
